      },
      {
        "id": "v1-routing-scope",
        "decision": "First release ships guild-default routing only. The social_channel_routes table is created but route management admin commands are out of scope. Channel-specific routes can be seeded via direct DB operations.",
        "rationale": "Keeps scope bounded while leaving the table structure ready for future per-channel routing admin tooling."
